# NF UI checklist — mandatory (no exceptions)

**Before any UI, form, www, or app surface change:**

1. Read `docs/www/NF_UI_BUILD_CHECKLIST_LOCKED_v1.md`
2. Read `docs/www/NF_WWW_LANGUAGE_LAYERS_LOCKED_v1.md`
3. Read `docs/DESIGN_REFERENCE_GOALS_LOCKED_v1.md` (R1–R8 minimum)

**After edits — fail-closed:**

```bash
bash scripts/verify-ui-build-checklist.sh
```

## Language law (client-facing)

- **No invitation copy** — no design partner, scarcity invites, “join us” funnels
- **No founder jargon** on public www — W3, Lane SSOT, nurture SSOT, SourceA, REGISTRY.json, `docs/ops/` links
- Show system as **sample / sandbox / demo** only — not ASF factory process

## Build law

- Marketing hubs: `python3 scripts/rebuild-www-v6.py` only
- Three contract SKUs only on www
- Stable CTAs: Apply for pilot · Start sandbox · Request Trust Brief

**Do not ship UI if `verify-ui-build-checklist` fails.**
